{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"c5a0f56194","title":"湘人斤张敬尧破坏和平","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"f9ee7df670","index":0,"year":1920,"month":6,"day":5,"articleId":"c5a0f56194"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji2","name":"毛泽东全集第2卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji2.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji2":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"a16da74ca4","type":"paragraph","text":"湘人斤张敬尧破坏和平","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji2","articleId":"c5a0f56194"},{"id":"db84b3f860","type":"paragraph","text":"（1920年6月5日）各报馆各团体公鉴：项湘南总司令部由广州转来艳电，称自吴师长撤防，三方签约。凡湘军采办粮袜，仍照前约履行，不得留难。证省日我军派人购米，经过防线，突被张敬尧接防军开枪轰击，伤捷我兵共计十三名，我军忍无可忍，不得不正当防御。似此自彼闻，破坏和平应由张敬尧负责。希转告全国静候公判等语，窃张敬尧涡湘，中外威知。今尤蓄意挑鲜，抚乱大局，资有做归。应请主张正谊，铲除强权，不胜迫切待命之至。","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji2","articleId":"c5a0f56194"},{"id":"f6eaf0ab3a","type":"paragraph","text":"湖南旅沪各界联合会邮","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji2","articleId":"c5a0f56194"}],"page":{"id":"f9a0f219c1","publicationId":"maoquanji2","articleId":"c5a0f56194","start":213,"end":213}}}},"__N_SSG":true}